parsed_email.subject: Re: Thalassini Voy.50 // Isdemir for discharging - CTM
parsed_email.body_text:
Message: 7436403
From: Cerrahgil Agency <agency@cerrahgil.com.tr>
To: Operations - Astra Shipmanagement Inc <ops@astraship.com>
Date: Thu, 27/Feb/2025 12:48:51 (UTC: +02:00)
Subject: Re: Thalassini Voy.50 // Isdemir for discharging - CTM

Dear Dimitra,

 

Good day,

 

Many thanks for your below, we will do the needful and arrange the said CTM with the provided denomination (as much as possible, according to banks availability). Costs are as follows ;

Please kindly see below estimated expenses for delivering 35000 CTM at Isdemir port  ;

 

CTM AMOUNT

35000 $

BANK COMMISSION          

175 $

DELIVERY FEE

200 $

SECURITY / INSURANCE     

200 $

TOTAL

35575 $


Our USD account details as follows :

  

BENEFICIARY

CERRAHGIL GEMI ACENTELIGI VE HIZMETLERI A.S.

BANKERS

QNB FINANSBANK A.S.

SWIFT

FNNBTRISXXX

US IBAN NO

TR79 0011 1000 0000 0030 9960 18

USD ACC NO

30996018

 

* Once total amount reflected our bank accounts, we can arrange the delivery of the requested CTM amount to the vessel.
* Please also note that some of the banknotes may have a security check stamp and this is normal and common practice in Turkey and Med, therefore if the same does not accept, we do not have an option to change with a new ones.
*Please be informed that there is an ongoing region-wide shortage of foreign currency at the banks in Iskenderun region.

Due to this, the 35000 USD amount will be collected from various banks within the region as no single branch is currently able to provide the full amount by itself.

For the above reasons, we would greatly appreciate if the CTM amount is remitted around 7 work days before vessel's arrival.

Many thanks in advance for your usual understanding.


P.S. : If denomination known please mention it asap because reserving small currencies (5,10,20 banknotes) by bank takes more time than usual.

Hope above will be satisfactory.

Best Regards,

Zafer Ulas Oskan
Agency Operations



CERRAHGIL SHIP AGENCIES AND SERVICES CO. LTD.
Address: Balmumcu Mahallesi,
Morbasan Sokak, Koza Is Merkezi C Blok,
No:14 Kat: 5 34349 Besiktas, Istanbul/TURKEY
Phone    : +90 212 232 47 00
Fax    : +90 212 231 00 35
Mobile    : +90 553 655 33 10
E-Mail    : agency@cerrahgil.com.tr
Web    : www.cerrahgil.com.tr


Join us on LinkedIN

 

 

From: Operations - Astra Shipmanagement Inc <ops@astraship.com>

Sent: 27.02.2025 12:47:47

To: agency@cerrahgil.com.tr

Subject: Thalassini Voy.50 // Isdemir for discharging - CTM

 

Message Number: 679421

From: ops@astraship.com

To: CERRAHGIL ISTANBUL (agency@cerrahgil.com.tr)

Sent: Thursday, Feb 27, 2025 11:47 (UTC +02:00)

Subject: Thalassini Voy.50 // Isdemir for discharging - CTM



Dear Oguz, 

 

Good Day.

 

Please note that our good vessel MV Thalassini will be calling Isdemir on abt mid of March and Owners intend to arrange the delivery of USD 35,000 as CTM.

Therefore, kindly revert with availability and related expenses.

 

Best Regards,
Dimitra Ioannidou
Operations Dept.

Astra Shipmanagement Inc
(as agents only)
6 Vouliagmenis Avenue & 12 Nirvana St.
Voula, 166 73
Athens - Greece
Tel: +30 213 0175 106

Prioritizing the wellbeing of our planet and its people.
